Linux instructions
==================

Informations to build numfftw3, a Python wrapper between Numeric and
FFTW version 3

To build numfftw3, type the following commands :

swig -python  -I/usr/local/include/python2.4 numfftw3.i

rm *.o *.so

gcc -fPIC -c numfftw3_wrap.c -I/usr/local/include/python2.4

ld -shared -lfftw3_threads -lfftw3 -lfftw3f_threads -lfftw3f -lm -lpthread numfftw3_wrap.o -o _numfftw3module.so
